{"tid":1425754,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［香城Online] 以後我地派物資，可以考慮咁做。","createTime":"2019-08-06T20:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T04:08:14.000Z","uid":291909,"like":80,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"70ae93a92e6dbe588b78127fc4f6b77e512fe8fb","tid":1425754,"uid":291909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:22:25.000Z","msg":"我發現家下每個人最機本都要有以下呢d裝備。<br />\n<br />\n基本裝1（新手村出生至進階）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qtsKA8p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqtsKA8p.png&h=cb72aa8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n進階裝1 （中前線玩家）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4PbfHOx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4PbfHOx.png&h=1c28ef53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補包袋1（全部玩家）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G4RGDm4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG4RGDm4.png&h=df5e321f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補包袋2（全部玩家）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MArfHOO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMArfHOO.png&h=b2906b91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">最重要係：要一set咁裝好哂！一包包咁比前線</span>，一黎快，二黎方便。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FyqzYnM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFyqzYnM.png&h=6c639189&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9o0syV7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9o0syV7.png&h=f3d5c665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我發現「咬淡蘋果」商城既裝都唔錯，循環再用，裝到成套裝。<br />\n<br />\n缺點係：<span style=\"color: red;\">有少少透光</span><br />\n解決方案：<span style=\"color: red;\">加d報紙之類既野擋一擋</span><br />\n<br />\n同時我希望大家唔好浪費物資！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真係唔該唔好浪費，當我求下你地</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為物資都好貴，家下都開始難買、同買唔到、缺貨等等。<br />\n<br />\n我每次發夢後都會周圍行，咩住一個紅白藍膠袋，可以重用都會重用，之後下次以螞蟻搬家嘅形式，比番前線。<br />\n<br />\n因為大家都怕比狗咬，所以扔哂d 物資。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">盡諒plz!</span><br />\n<br />\n糧草同裝備係好重要資源黎！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以上既裝備都適用對另一條支線：白色的三合會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cf28c04a0a8d88ae6a6bb8f7b9d531c953589c","tid":1425754,"uid":291909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:23:11.000Z","msg":"自推！唔好浪費"},{"pid":"ab916b274363f39dae049c3a4cc193aeea2b3511","tid":1425754,"uid":7223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:24:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f48a3627be8eb3e03497229f034c800c1935c1bb","tid":1425754,"uid":291909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:26:21.000Z","msg":"推x10"},{"pid":"6e7b2d44c66d947dd40456ea1a69813ef6c75ea3","tid":1425754,"uid":291909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:26:34.000Z","msg":"推x9"},{"pid":"83771e561fbe503c44fd26a08d77c3bbcbc4df0b","tid":1425754,"uid":291909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:27:18.000Z","msg":"推x8"},{"pid":"5204b5fae2a6ebd496ec1a1eed87aba01eb74c52","tid":1425754,"uid":291909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T20:27:52.000Z","msg":"推x7"},{"pid":"b75236b005d4af23fd340aa9ddb8e9985d348752","tid":1425